title: R.I. urged to find its economic niche
text: PROVIDENCE, R.I. — Business journalist Ron Insana told a crowd of business, political and education leaders Monday night that the U.S. economy — what he called "fortress America" — is moving forward and still " the economy to watch. " The keynote speaker at the Rhode Island Public Expenditure Council's 72nd annual meeting, Insana is very familiar with Rhode Island and visits Newport frequently, he said in an interview.
